==B==
{{Glossary}}
{{term|term= Berlese funnel |content= [[Berlese funnel]] }}{{defn|1= 
{{ghat|1=see also [[#Winkler extraction|Winkler extraction]]}}
device used to extract ants and other living organism from soil and [[leaf-litter]] samples; a sample is placed on a screen with a funnel beneath, and a heat source above; the drying forces the animals downwards, where they fall into a collecting jar, usually filled with alcohol<ref name="Majer_et_al_2000"/> }}

{{term|term= bivouac |content= [[Bivouac (ants)|bivouac]] }}{{defn|1= in [[Army ant|army]] and [[Dorylus|driver ants]], nest formed by the bodies of the ants themselves to protect the queen and larvae<ref name="Majer_et_al_2000"/> }}
{{Glossary end}}

