==T==
{{Glossary}}
{{term|term= tandem running |content= [[tandem running]] }}{{defn|1= 
{{ghat|1=see also [[#pheromone trail|pheromone trail]]}}
recruitment method used by some species of ants, where one ant leads a single, closely following nestmate to a target (usually food)<ref name="Planque_et_al_2010"/> }}

{{term|term= trail pheromone |content= trail pheromone }}{{defn|1= 
see ''[[#pheromone trail|pheromone trail]]'' }}

