}}
{{Glossary end}}

==W==
{{Glossary}}
{{term|term= Winkler extraction |content= [[Winkler extraction]] }}{{defn|1= 
{{ghat|1=see also [[#Berlese funnel|Berlese funnel]]}}
device used to extract ants and other living organism from soil and [[leaf-litter]] samples; a sample is placed inside an inner bag constructed from cloth mesh, which is suspended in a second bag containing a funnel leading to a collecting jar, usually filled with alcohol; the device is hung up in the air and passively extracts escaping animals<ref name="Majer_et_al_2000"/> }}

{{Glossary end}}

